These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-1::.
There 5 different types of food: tomato, raspberry, onion, cranberry, grapes
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, rock, classical, jazz, ambient
1. the fan of jazz is in an odd position##4
2. the fan of jazz is in the middle##1
3. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the person eating onion is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
5. the person eating tomato is between the fan of jazz and the fan of classical##2
6. the person eating grapes is in the middle##1
7. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
8. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person eating grapes##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |   3    |    4    |    5    |
| Food          | raspberry | tomato | grapes | cranberry | onion |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | ambient      | jazz   | dubstep     | rock    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-2::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, mirinda, juice, milk, 7up
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: golf, weightlifting, rowing, volleyball, skiing
1. the person drinking coffee is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in the middle##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person drinking 7up##3
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person drinking juice and the person who's sport is volleyball##2
6. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
7. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |     2     |    3     |      4      |    5    |
| Beverage   | juice     | milk       | 7up    | coffee | mirinda   |
| Sport      | weightlifting | golf | volleyball | skiing      | rowing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-3::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, dancing, drawing, rock-climbing
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: funk, classical, d&b, dubstep, country
1. the fan of dubstep is the person who's hobby is chess##1
2. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
3. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of d&b##1
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
5. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the fan of funk##3
6. the fan of country is on the left or right of the fan of classical##3
7. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
8. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3      |     4      |      5      |
| Hobby         | chess | dancing | sudoku | drawing    | rock-climbing |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep     | funk        | d&b      | classical | country      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-4::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: reading, writing, collecting, card-games, dancing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, family, romance, sports, crime
1. the person who's hobby is collecting is in the middle##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is in an even position##4
3. the person watching family movies is on the far right##1
4. the person who's hobby is dancing is the person watching family movies##1
5. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is between the person watching romance movies and the person who's hobby is dancing##2
7. the person watching crime movies is the person who's hobby is card-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |       3       |     4     |      5       |
| Hobby         | reading      | card-games | collecting | writing   | dancing  |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | crime    | romance        | thriller | family |

