.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-5::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, water, almond-milk, juice
There are 5 different nationalities: spanish, colombian, polish, dutch, german
1. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the spanish##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the german##1
4. the polish is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
5. the german is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the dutch##1
7. the colombian is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking water is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |     4     |    5     |
| Beverage      | juice      | hot-chocolate | fanta   | almond-milk  | water  |
| Nationality   | polish | dutch | spanish | colombian | german |

