.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-6::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea, fanta, water, juice
The people have 5 different jobs:  entrepreneur, accountant, chef, doctor, manager
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
2. the accountant is between the manager and the person drinking fanta##2
3. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the accountant##1
5. the chef is the person drinking fanta##1
6. the chef is in an even position##4
7. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person drinking coffee##3
8. the doctor is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |         2          |    3     |     4     |       5        |
| Beverage   | iced-tea        | coffee                | water  | fanta  | juice            |
| Job        | entrepreneur | manager | accountant | chef | doctor |

