.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-7::.
There are 5 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, cola, almond-milk, tea, juice
The people have 5 different jobs:  chef, analyst, software-developer, coach, project-manager
1. the person drinking tea is on the left or right of the analyst##3
2. the project-manager is on the left or right of the analyst##3
3. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
4. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
5. the software-developer is in an odd position##4
6. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1
7. the chef is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
8. the project-manager is on the right of the analyst##1
9. the coach is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |   2    |      3      |     4     |       5       |
| Beverage   | juice       | almond-milk   | cola    | tea    | iced-tea |
| Job        | software-developer | chef | analyst | project-manager | coach     |

