The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: time-travel, thriller, epic, crime, satire
1. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
3. the person drinking 7up is in an even position##4
4. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
5. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching crime movies and the person watching satire movies##2
6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
7. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |     3      |    4    |    5    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk  | fanta       | iced-tea      | 7up  | almond-milk   |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | time-travel | crime | thriller | epic |

