.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-9::.
There are 5 different nationalities: british, colombian, malaysian, japanese, spanish
5 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, snake, bird, ferret
1. the owner of the rat is in an even position##4
2. the japanese is the owner of the bird##1
3. the owner of the bird is the japanese##1
4. the japanese is on the far right##1
5. the colombian is the owner of the rat##1
6. the malaysian is between the colombian and the british##2
7. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the malaysian##1
8. the owner of the hamster is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |     3      |    4    |     5      |
| Nationality   | spanish | colombian | malaysian     | british | japanese |
| Pet           | hamster | rat     | snake | ferret    | bird      |

