The people prefer 5 different types of sport: skiing, baseball, ice-hockey, water-polo, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the architect##1
2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is baseball is the scientist##1
4. the person who's sport is skiing is on the right of the scientist##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is in an odd position##4
6. the architect is on the left of the chef##1
7. the writer is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |   2    |      3      |     4      |    5    |
| Job     | architect | chef | writer | scientist | dressmaker |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | badminton | water-polo    | baseball    | skiing  |

