.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-11::.
There 5 different types of food: grapefruit, carrot, papaya, apricot, asparagus
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: water-polo, biathlon, weightlifting, climbing, rugby
1. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
2. the person eating grapefruit is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
3. the person eating grapefruit is between the person who's sport is weightlifting and the person who's sport is biathlon##2
4. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person who's sport is rugby is the person eating papaya##1
6. the person who's sport is rugby is in an odd position##4
7. the person eating carrot is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |    2     |       3       |     4      |   5    |
| Food    | carrot    | asparagus  | grapefruit      | apricot     | papaya |
| Sport   | water-polo | biathlon | climbing | weightlifting | rugby |

