.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-12::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, grapes, grapefruit, carrot, pomegranate
The people use 5 different means of transport: subway, bike, van, tram, roller
1. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the van##1
2. the person driving the roller is the person eating asparagus##1
3. the person driving the roller is in the middle##1
4. the person eating grapes is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
5. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person driving the subway is between the person driving the roller and the person eating grapes##2
7. the person driving the bike is in an odd position##4
8. the person driving the bike is on the far left##1
9. the person driving the roller is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |   3   |     4     |     5      |
| Food        | carrot | pomegranate | asparagus  | grapefruit | grapes     |
| Transport   | bike  | van     | roller | subway      | tram |

