There are 5 different nationalities: polish, brazilian, malaysian, egyptian, russian
1. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
3. the egyptian is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
6. the person drinking almond-milk is between the polish and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
7. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
8. the polish is on the left of the malaysian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage      | juice       | hot-chocolate | almond-milk | lemonade   | water   |
| Nationality   | egyptian | brazilian | russian  | polish | malaysian |

