.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-14::.
There 5 different types of food: asparagus, apple, blueberry, kiwi, eggplant
The people have 5 different hobbies: sudoku, rock-climbing, fishing, video-games, baking
1. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person eating eggplant is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
5. the person eating apple is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the left or right of the person eating blueberry##3
7. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is rock-climbing and the person eating apple##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3      |     4     |     5      |
| Food    | eggplant   | kiwi  | apple     | asparagus | blueberry |
| Hobby   | sudoku | fishing | baking | video-games | rock-climbing      |

