.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: thriller, western, zombie, sports, spy
There are 5 different nationalities: spanish, mexican, indian, russian, thai
1. the spanish is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the russian##3
3. the spanish is on the left of the indian##1
4. the indian is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the mexican is on the left or right of the person watching sports movies##3
6. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person watching western movies##3
7. the indian is in an odd position##4
8. the russian is in the middle##1
9. the mexican is on the right of the person watching western movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3       |    4     |    5    |
| Movie-Genre   | western  | zombie    | sports | thriller   | spy |
| Nationality   | thai | mexican | russian    | spanish | indian |

