.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-17::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: dubstep, blues, folk, classical, punk
The people use 5 different means of transport: car, jet-ski, ship, boat, trike
1. the fan of classical is the person driving the jet-ski##1
2. the fan of classical is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the person driving the boat is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of punk is between the fan of blues and the person driving the car##2
5. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
7. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
8. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of blues##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |    3     |    4    |   5   |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | classical | folk     | punk     | blues |
| Transport     | boat   | jet-ski   | car | ship | trike  |

