.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-18::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: crime, romance, action, family, comedy
The people use 5 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, roller, trike, bike
1. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
2. the person driving the quad-bike is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
5. the person watching romance movies is on the left or right of the person driving the trike##3
6. the person driving the bike is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person driving the quad-bike##3
8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
9. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2       |     3      |   4    |     5      |
| Movie-Genre   | crime | romance | comedy     | action | family |
| Transport     | trike       | quad-bike   | roller | bus   | bike        |

