5. the person who's hobby is video-games is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the argentine##2
6. the egyptian is between the person who's hobby is fishing and the argentine##2
7. the turkish is in an odd position##4
8. the argentine is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |     3      |    4    |     5      |
