.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: folk, r&b, jazz, d&b, funk
The people use 5 different means of transport: van, helicopter, roller, bus, car
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of funk##1
2. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of funk##1
3. the person driving the helicopter is between the person driving the car and the person driving the bus##2
4. the person driving the roller is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of d&b is in the middle##1
6. the person driving the car is the fan of folk##1
7. the fan of r&b is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |  3   |    4     |     5      |
| Music-Genre   | folk | jazz      | d&b | funk     | r&b      |
| Transport     | car | helicopter | bus | van | roller |

 